songs.title: The Breakdown
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
Hey you, turn around
Let it break you down, let it break you down
Hey you, burning now
Let 'em take you down, let 'em take you down

[Verse]
I went in the creek
Put the salt right on the leech
I went right into the teeth, of the beast
Made 'em scream out "you don't belong here"
I went in the creek
Put the salt right on the leash
I went right into the teeth, of the beast
Made 'em scream out "you don't belong here"
